    Dine-in

    We take walk-ins or reservations. Either way, see the host or hostess when you arrive.

    Reservation policy:

    • All members of your party must be present before you can be seated. 

    • Reservations are not required but strongly suggested, especially for larger parties or weekend nights. 

    • For parties of 6 or more we can only split the bill a maximum of 6 even ways. These larger parties are also subject to an auto gratuity.

    • There is a $15 fee to bring your own cake and our staff to serve it

    • We do not take reservations specifically for our outside tables due to the unpredictable weather. Outside tables and bar stools are first come first serve.

    • A credit card is required to be held when you dine with us outside
